Interface CustomStrategyRepository

  • All Superinterfaces:

    @Repository
 @Transactional
public interface CustomStrategyRepository
extends org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<CustomStrategyEntity,java.lang.Long>
    This interface offers methods to retrieve data from the custom strategy table in the database.
